```

Adds a request and returns its queue ID.

##### `process(maxRequests?)`

```typescript
process(maxRequests?: number): Array<PathRequestQueueEntry<TRequest, TResult>>
```

Processes up to `maxRequests` queued items in FIFO order. Defaults to `1`.

##### `clearPending()`

```typescript
